title: Taking Additional Steps With Respect to the Situation in the Western Balkans
summary: President Biden has issued an executive order to take additional steps regarding the situation in the Western Balkans. The order includes blocking property and interests in property of individuals involved in actions that threaten peace, security, stability, or territorial integrity in the region. It also targets those engaged in corruption and human rights abuses. The order amends previous executive orders and is subject to applicable law and available appropriations.
